Package Question4

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    driver
    instantiate a job which will run map reduce It allows the user to configure the job, submit it, control its execution, and query the state.
    map
    for finding the top 10 orders over the years based on total profit, we created tree maps for total profit and placed the data associated with it in the tree the idea is to use Mappers to find local top 10 records, as there can be many Mappers running parallely on different blocks of data of a file.
    reduce
    Reducer processes one key-value pair at a time and writes them as final output on HDFS.
